data.description: Hurry Home to this wonderful Prairie Village ranch home located in the popular Prairie Fields community! You'll love belonging to this great community that offers easy access to schools, parks, shopping, & dining. Before entering the home, you will be captivated by the lush yard, mature trees, gorgeous landscaping and relaxing water feature. You will also notice the newer (2022) roof that includes new decking and front gutters. When you step inside you will be greeted with warmth and charm. The home has gorgeous wood floors throughout the living room, dining room, 3 bedrooms, primary bath and hall bath. Soothing colors adorn the walls and charming ceiling beams add to the beauty of the living room, dining room, kitchen and family room. The U-shaped kitchen is open to the dining room, overlooks the family room and offers beautiful butcher block counters, a tile floor and plenty of room to fix dinner for family and friends. The huge family room has a beautiful fireplace and brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring, that also extends down the stairs and through the finished lower level. The finished lower level offers so many possibilities...a play room, media room, exercise room, office, family room, hobby room, 4th non-conforming bedroom, etc. Additionally, it has a back staircase that goes to the 2-car garage! Off the main level family room, you can step into the fenced backyard oasis. You will spend many days and evenings relaxing and making memories around the built-in firepit, all while being serenaded by a tranquil Koi pond. And, for easy upkeep to this lush oasis, the property has an irrigation system. This home has so much to offer and is a 'must see'! Get ready to fall in love with your new home! Due to feedback the first weekend on the market, the sellers decided to have a structural engineer inspect the back family room that was added to the home by a previous owner. All info is available in Supplements.
